text:
A nice but also intense stream today. :_ハート:
Started with a wonderful BGM

And this marks Rushia's return to APEX Legends.
She made more attracting the gameplay.
Mainly, forgetting these bad experiences at May 2020 (Private) and July 2020 with only laughing everytime.
That would be the beginning of the best from Rushia. :_ちょうちょ:

Best place global and today: 2nd place.

Maybe she needs help from experienced Holomembers, like Towa-chan and Botan-chan, but all indicates she's also training for her own way. :_きゅん:

So that's she needs: more laughing at Gameplay when things becoming bad or worse. :_るんるん: Never giving up.
